要連續返29日工先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61c2a3feb7642a62d1689907d113c79a3465a5c","tid":435142,"uid":60529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:02:25.000Z","msg":"咁人地叫勤工津貼喎<br />\n遲到請假就唔叫勤工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e7b382baeb2e24672aa4c28ccd659ecde8da7b","tid":435142,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"我公司連咁易拎既獎金都冇呀"},{"pid":"45fe0cd6ea81dd21b0681ceb55293e2c4ec72128","tid":435142,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其他公司又唔見有問題？<br />\n<br />\n真係得華人賤種做管理層既公司特別多問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n前老細係鬼佬喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n前前前前前前前"},{"pid":"57f0723aa19aec1b02e73a63f3ab2e63bb8a15e5","tid":435142,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:10:30.000Z","msg":"大部份公司勤工都係一個月咁計"},{"pid":"67d8e7f99db9adcbdbb95ae7cc7dd9c1a7588571","tid":435142,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大部份公司勤工都係一個月咁計</blockquote><br />\n人地起碼有固定返工時間<br />\n<br />\n做FA冇架 得閒返早 得返成個通宵都要返<br />\n咁樣嘅生活其實好易病"}]}